disposition_summary.Rd

Subject disposition overview

Usage

disposition_summary(sdtm_data)

Arguments

sdtm_data

SDTM data object.

Value

A data frame

Examples

disposition_summary(examplinib_sad)
#>    ACTARMCD ONGOING  N
#> 1        C1   FALSE  3
#> 2       C10   FALSE 12
#> 3        C2   FALSE  3
#> 4        C3   FALSE  3
#> 5        C4   FALSE  3
#> 6        C5   FALSE  6
#> 7        C6   FALSE  3
#> 8        C7   FALSE  6
#> 9        C8   FALSE  6
#> 10       C9   FALSE  3
#> 11 SCRNFAIL      NA 17
